::Shredder::

Shredder shakes his head at Mantella's transmission. "I'm fine. I'm at the 
base." he replies, heading toward the CR chambers and limping slightly.

He grins to himself as he hears Mantella's last sentence. Everyone was glad 
to come (adult joke there), but why was she offering him help? He shruggs, 
continuing toward the CR chambers.
